my actual hiking tent will be here on the 14th. Zeus exo 2. Excited hope it's a good one. I had the zeus exo one tried it a couple times loved it, but was stolen before I could get any real use out of it.
once the tent arrives I'll go spend a couple days with my kids, then it Georgia bound. See what the mountains bring me.
waiting on my last piece of equipment to come in so having to push my Start date.
